MINCED CHICKEN

1½	cups minced cooked chicken
1 	hard-cooked egg
½	tsp. grated onion
⅓	cup mayonnaise
	Salt and pepper
	Merita Thin-Sliced Bread
	Merita Wheat Bread

Combine minced chicken, riced or sieved hard-cooked egg, seasonings and mayonnaise. Spread Merita Thin-Sliced Bread with soft butter or margarine; add filling and cover with buttered bread. Trim crusts; cut in small squares, triangles, strips, etc., or cut bread with fancy cutters; spread with butter, filling and cover as above. Makes about 75 sandwiches. 